citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:40 pm on 17-
NOV-2022. A person in the residence said the licensee was gone and would not be back for a few hours. There was no
answer to a call to the licensee's mobile phone.
End Section
